<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBeck2003">Beck, Kent (2003). <i>Test-Driven Development By Example</i>. Boston: Addison Wesley. pp.&#160;144–5. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0321146530" class="internal">ISBN 0-321-14653-0</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Test-Driven+Development+By+Example&amp;rft.aulast=Beck&amp;rft.aufirst=Kent&amp;rft.au=Beck%2C+Kent&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B144%E2%80%935&amp;rft.place=Boston&amp;rft.pub=Addison+Wesley&amp;rft.isbn=0-321-14653-0&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mock_object"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
